---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-12">
    <div class="glass-panel p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl">
      <h1
        class="text-4xl font-display font-bold mb-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-accent to-brand-primary bg-clip-text text-transparent"
      >
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>

      <div
        class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none prose-headings:font-display prose-a:text-brand-accent hover:prose-a:text-brand-primary"
      >
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-8 border-b border-white/10 pb-4">
          Last Updated: 2026-01-31
        </p>

        <p>
          Thank you for visiting Gin's Blog. We respect your privacy and are
          committed to protecting your personal data. This privacy policy
          explains what information we collect and how we use it.
        </p>
        <p class="italic text-gray-400">
          感谢您访问 Gin
          的博客。我们尊重您的隐私并致力于保护您的个人数据。本隐私政策说明了我们收集的信息及其用途。
        </p>

        <h3>1. Information We Collect / 我们收集的信息</h3>

        <h4>1.1 Automatically Collected Data / 自动收集的数据</h4>
        <p>
          When you visit our site, we may collect minimal technical data to
          optimize your experience and ensure security:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>
            <strong>Network Info / 网络信息</strong>: IP address, ISP,
            connection type (e.g., WiFi/4G) for routing optimization.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Adaptive UX Metrics / 体验优化指标</strong>: Screen
            resolution, device memory, and connection quality to determine
            optimal content rendering.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Location Data / 位置数据</strong>: Approximate location
            (City/Country) derived from IP address for analytics purposes.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h4>1.2 User Account Data / 用户账户数据</h4>
        <p>
          If you choose to log in via third-party OAuth providers (GitHub,
          Google, Discord), we store only the public information provided by
          them:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>Username / 用户名</li>
          <li>Public Email Address / 公开电子邮件地址</li>
          <li>Avatar URL / 头像链接</li>
          <li>Third-party User ID / 第三方用户 ID</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>2. How We Use Your Data / 我们如何使用您的数据</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>
            <strong>Performance Optimization / 性能优化</strong>: Metrics help
            us serve lighter content to slower connections.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Security / 安全防护</strong>: IP addresses are used to
            detect routing anomalies and prevent abuse.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Social Features / 社交功能</strong>: Your account data
            allows you to post comments and interact with content.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div
          class="bg-brand-primary/10 border-l-4 border-brand-primary p-4 my-4"
        >
          <p class="font-bold m-0 p-0 text-white">
            We do NOT share your personal data with advertisers or third
            parties.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm m-0 p-0 text-gray-400 mt-1">
            我们不会与广告商或第三方共享您的个人数据。
          </p>
        </div>

        <h3>3. Data Storage / 数据存储</h3>
        <p>
          Your data is stored securely on <strong>Cloudflare D1 & KV</strong> infrastructure.
          We employ industry-standard security measures including strict access controls
          (Zero Trust) and encryption.
        </p>
        <p class="italic text-gray-400">
          您的数据安全地存储在 Cloudflare D1 & KV
          基础设施上。我们采取行业标准的安全措施，包括严格的访问控制（零信任）和加密。
        </p>

        <h3>4. Your Rights / 您的权利</h3>
        <p>
          You have full control over your data. Upon request, or by using the
          "Logout & Clear Session" features in the user interface, you can
          manage your session data.
        </p>

        <hr class="border-white/10 my-8" />

        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
          This project is open source. You can audit the code at <a
            href="https://github.com/IchimaruGin728/Gins-Blog"
            target="_blank">GitHub Repository</a
          >.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
